<p>Emacs is amazingly alive. New packages are regularly listed on <a href="http://melpa.org">melpa</a> and a new book just came out: <a href="https://www.masteringemacs.org/book">Mastering Emacs</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/mickeynp">Mickey Petersen</a>.</p>
